How to handle configuration:

-- No commandline options other than configFile --

Create "default" configurations on first install:
* dcrd:
- rpc user/pass set to USER/PASSWORD
- rpc host/port (127.0.0.1:9109)

* dcrwallet:
- appdata: cwd (userAppData/wallets/thisWallet)
- rpc user/pass set to USER/PASSWORD
- tlscurve: "P-256",
- noinitialload: "1",
- onetimetlskey: "1",
- rpcconnect to match dcrd (127.0.0.1:9109)
- rpc host/port (127.0.0.1:9121)
- rpccert loc
- enableticketbuyer: 0

* dcrctl:
- rpc user/pass set to USER/PASSWORD
- rpcconnect to match dcrd (127.0.0.1:9109)
- dcrd rpccert loc

When changed to testnet (and back to mainnet): 
*dcrd:
- add testnet flag (remove any testnet flag)

*dcrwallet:
- add testnet flag (remove any testnet flag)

*dcrctl: 
- add testnet flag (remove any testnet flag)


